^B@2^*Bhondo717:^*N|cp||at| With modern bidding, there are many variations of how to show support. aggie has 3 ways to show support:
with a limit raise, 2@C, as she did;
with 3 card support and less than a limit raise, she can bid 2@S;
and with 4 card support, she should usually bid 3@S, with less than a limit raise.
